
first install mongo and then robomongo => 1 step

npm init is used to see the package which are used..
npm install mongodb@2.2.5 --save is used to connect mongodb server with node js

In other db first we need to create a database and then we can connect. but in mongo we no need to create database
first we can connect and then we can create

eventhrough we create a db in mongo , it wont be visible until we write some data on it

27017 is a port number that is visible on robomongo
